              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Machine Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-text-base/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Random Forest Regressors predict finger movements from pressure data.
            The LASK5 labeling device captures ground-truth training data.
            Python pipelines process UDP sensor streams in real time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Community Driven -->
        <div class="card group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange-light/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-orange-light transition-colors">
